title: Express Burn Plus v4.15
description:
Express Burn Plus v4.15

Express Burn is a program for Windows that lets you create and record CDs with any PC with a CD burner installed. With Express Burn you can record a CD, DVD, High Definition DVD or Blu-ray disc quickly and easily by dragging the files you want onto the Express Burn icon and clicking 'Burn'. The software then does the rest, including converting the files if required. It is also the fastest CD/DVD writing program in the world using proprietary optimizing systems. Version 4.13 is a bug fixing release.
